source.name: Debt Position and Activity Report
source.description: The Debt Position and Activity Report shows the current and historical debt position of the U.S. Department of the Treasury in relation to debt held by the public, intragovernmental holdings, and statutory debt limit. Issue and redemption activity are also provided in this report.
